Welcome to your new blog! This theme is a SvelteKit implementation inspired by the beautiful [Duckquill](https://duckquill.daudix.one) theme for Zola.

## Features

This blog comes with everything you need to start writing:

- **Markdown support** with frontmatter for metadata
- **Syntax highlighting** for code blocks
- **Light/dark mode** with system preference detection
- **Responsive design** that looks great on any device
- **Fast** static site generation

## Writing Posts

Creating a new post is simple. Just add a `.md` file to the `src/posts` directory with the following frontmatter:

```markdown
---
title: Your Post Title
date: "2025-01-07"
description: A brief description
tags:
  - tag1
  - tag2
---

Your content here...
```

## Code Highlighting

Code blocks are automatically highlighted:

```javascript
function greet(name) {
  console.log(`Hello, ${name}!`);
}

greet('World');
```

## What's Next?

1. Customize the site config in `src/lib/config.ts`
2. Update the about page
3. Start writing your first real post!

Happy blogging! 🦆
